description: The 13-year-old was found clinging to cliffs near Onchan before being pulled to safety by the coastguard.
title: Isle of Man teenager rescued from cliff face near Onchan
title_page: Isle of Man teenager rescued from cliff face near Onchan - BBC News
maintext: The coastguard spokesman issued a warning following the incident, saying said people should "consider the safety of their actions" and "not put themselves in a dangerous situation".
